{
  "id": "L16",
  "title": "Returning a Faulty Product",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "In this lesson, you'll learn how to return a product that is 'roto' (broken) to a store, 'la tienda'."
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V01",
      "data": {
        "La tienda": "The store"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E01",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Hola",
        "meaning": "Hello"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E02",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Perdón",
        "meaning": "Excuse me"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V02",
      "data": {
        "Una pregunta": "A question"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V03",
      "data": {
        "Un producto": "A product"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E03",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Tengo una pregunta",
        "meaning": "I have a question"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "pronunciation",
      "item_id": "L16_P01",
      "data": {
        "word": "Pregunta",
        "phonetic": "pre-GUN-ta",
        "tip": "The stress is on the second-to-last syllable: 'gun'."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V04",
      "data": {
        "La cafetera": "The coffee machine"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V05",
      "data": {
        "La semana pasada": "Last week"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V06",
      "data": {
        "Aquí": "Here"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E04",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "(Yo) compré",
        "meaning": "I bought"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "Adjectives change to match a noun's gender. For 'la cafetera' (feminine), you use 'rota'. For a masculine noun like 'el teléfono', you use 'roto'."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E05",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Está rota",
        "meaning": "It is broken (feminine)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L16_S01",
      "title": "Explaining the problem",
      "setting": "You are in an electronics store with your broken coffee machine.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Approach the staff member",
          "chatbot_message": "Hola. ¿Puedo ayudar?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Explain you bought a product here",
          "chatbot_message": "Sí, claro. ¿Qué producto?"
        },
        {
          "title": "State that the product is broken",
          "chatbot_message": "Entiendo. ¿El problema?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E06",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Sí",
        "meaning": "Yes"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V07",
      "data": {
        "El ticket": "The receipt"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E07",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Aquí tiene el ticket",
        "meaning": "Here is the receipt"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "text": "'Quiero' means 'I want'. It is a direct but common way to ask for things in Spanish stores."
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E08",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "(Yo) quiero",
        "meaning": "I want"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V08",
      "data": {
        "Una nueva": "A new one (feminine)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V09",
      "data": {
        "O": "Or"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V10",
      "data": {
        "El dinero": "The money"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E09",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Mi dinero",
        "meaning": "My money"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L16_S02",
      "title": "Suggesting a solution",
      "setting": "You've explained the coffee machine is broken. Now you need to sort it out.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Show the receipt",
          "chatbot_message": "Oh, no. ¿Tiene el ticket?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Say you want a new one",
          "chatbot_message": "Gracias. ¿Qué quiere?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Alternatively, ask for your money",
          "chatbot_message": "Okay."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E10",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Gracias",
        "meaning": "Thank you"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V11",
      "data": {
        "Perfecto": "Perfect"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E11",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "De nada",
        "meaning": "You're welcome"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E12",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Todo bien",
        "meaning": "Everything's good"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "vocabulary",
      "item_id": "L16_V12",
      "data": {
        "La ayuda": "The help"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E13",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Gracias por la ayuda",
        "meaning": "Thanks for the help"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "expression",
      "item_id": "L16_E14",
      "data": {
        "phrase": "Adiós",
        "meaning": "Goodbye"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "interactive_scenario",
      "scenario_id": "L16_S03",
      "title": "Finishing the conversation",
      "setting": "The employee is going to help you. Time to wrap things up.",
      "conversation_flow": [
        {
          "title": "Respond to the solution",
          "chatbot_message": "Okay. Un momento... Sí, aquí tiene una cafetera nueva."
        },
        {
          "title": "Confirm everything is okay",
          "chatbot_message": "De nada. ¿Todo bien ahora?"
        },
        {
          "title": "Thank them and say goodbye",
          "chatbot_message": "Excelente."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}